      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AURUM BELLE (5) led and ran away to score very impressively on debut over this course and distance. The $725k purchase out of Stakes winner Dame Giselle looks to get a similar run in transit here and the form out of her debut has stacked up. Only rises 0.5kg and can get the job done again. HE'S A MACHINO (2) was very impressive on debut when winning by 1L before Christmas and bolted in at the trials recently at Lark Hill. Chris Parnham rides today and he has the speed to roll across from the wide draw. Can play a leading role once again. ALL ON RED (1) looks targeted towards this with two trials coming in. He gives his rivals weight after two impressive wins but it took a good one to beat him before the break. Can return in a positive note. SNOW MONKEY (7) was behind AURUM BELLE last time out and gets a weight swing in her favour. Can feature. INCREDIBLE MR FOX (4) looks the best of the debutants in this event.",
